content: We have lost over 125,000 family farms since Crooked Joe Biden, and his even more incompetent Vice President, Crazy Kamala Harris, took over our government. THEY HATE OUR FARMERS, AND WANT THEM DRIVEN OUT OF BUSINESS — WHICH IS EXACTLY WHAT THEY ARE DOING!!! FARMERS FOR TRUMP = MAGA2024! VOTE, VOTE, VOTE!!!
